<Heading Id="sizes" IsAnchor="true" Level="HeadingLevel.H3" MarginTop="Spacing.Five">Sizes</Heading>
<p>Buttons come in three different sizes.</p>

<Heading Id="sizes-large" IsAnchor="true" Level="HeadingLevel.H4" MarginTop="Spacing.Five">Large</Heading>
<Button Color="NamedColor.Primary" Size="ButtonSize.Large">Large button</Button>
